data.description: Welcome home to this well maintained first floor 2BR/2BA condominium conveniently located in the popular Midtown area and  is very near Novant Hospital, grocery shopping, dining, movie theatre and minutes from  Greenfield Lake and Historic Downtown Wilmington! This unit has new LVP flooring in bedrooms, refurbished hard wood floors in living area and cordless blinds.  You will love the 11ft X 8ft three season sunroom, which is perfect for a home office or just to relax with a cup of coffee. Previous updates include new windows, insulated sunroom with new floor, bathroom renovations include new vanity, floor, lighting and toilets.
